android.support.v4.media.session

Class MediaSessionCompat.Callback

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.media.session.MediaSessionCompat.Callback
  • Enclosing class:
    MediaSessionCompat

    public abstract static class MediaSessionCompat.Callback
extends java.lang.Object
    Receives transport controls, media buttons, and commands from controllers and the system. The callback may be set using MediaSessionCompat.setCallback(android.support.v4.media.session.MediaSessionCompat.Callback).

      • onCommand

        public void onCommand(java.lang.String command,
             Bundle extras,
             ResultReceiver cb)
        Called when a controller has sent a custom command to this session. The owner of the session may handle custom commands but is not required to.
        Parameters:
        command - The command name.
        extras - Optional parameters for the command, may be null.
        cb - A result receiver to which a result may be sent by the command, may be null.
